    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those looking for reliable transportation. While it is mechanically sound and drives well, it does show its age through various cosmetic imperfections, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It has been well-maintained under the hood, though a prospective buyer should expect the typical aesthetic wear-and-tear associated with its history. This is a solid, functional car that is ready for the road.",
