    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a fixer-upper or a reliable source of parts. While it has seen plenty of miles and definitely shows significant wear and tear both inside and out, it's a budget-friendly way to get your hands on a classic model. If you're handy with a wrench and looking for a diamond in the rough, this is the one for you!",
