    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for parts or as a dedicated project for someone with mechanical expertise. The engine struggles to turn over and likely requires a full rebuild, and the transmission is currently slipping significantly. Visually, the car has major rust issues along the frame and body panels, alongside several large dents and peeling clear coat. The interior is heavily worn with multiple tears in the seating and a non-functional climate control system; it will need to be towed from its current location.",
