    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit has been carefully vetted to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Representing a premier choice for the professional driver, it delivers a consistent and refined driving experience. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that exemplifies proven durability and exceptional value.",
      "price": 34850.0,
